n.org/doc/manuals/securing-debian-howto/ch9.en.html could be helpful to resolve the issue.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=tysonite","name":"tysonite","key":"tysonite","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Mikhail","active":true,"timeZone":"Etc/UTC"},"created":"2012-08-21T14:30:56.174+0000","updated":"2012-08-21T14:30:56.174+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12604210/comment/13475406","id":"13475406","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=ddossot","name":"ddossot","key":"ddossot","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?ownerId=ddossot&avatarId=25441","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&ownerId=ddossot&avatarId=25441","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&ownerId=ddossot&avatarId=25441","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&ownerId=ddossot&avatarId=25441"},"displayName":"David Dossot","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Vancouver"},"body":"For the sake of others having the same issue, I've been able to workaround the problem by running:\n\n{noformat}sudo groupadd -r hadoop\nsudo useradd --comment \"Hadoop MapReduce\" --shell /bin/bash -M -r --groups hadoop --home /var/lib/hadoop/mapred mapred\nsudo useradd --comment \"Hadoop HDFS\" --shell /bin/bash -M -r --groups hadoop --home /var/lib/hadoop/hdfs hdfs{noformat} ","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=ddossot","name":"ddossot","key":"ddossot","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?ownerId=ddossot&avatarId=25441","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&ownerId=ddossot&avatarId=25441","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&ownerId=ddossot&avatarId=25441","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&ownerId=ddossot&avatarId=25441"},"displayName":"David Dossot","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Vancouver"},"created":"2012-10-12T22:21:48.320+0000","updated":"2012-10-12T22:21:48.320+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12604210/comment/13868722","id":"13868722","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=lsomchai","name":"lsomchai","key":"lsomchai","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Somchai LIMSIRORATANA","active":true,"timeZone":"Asia/Jakarta"},"body":"In the preinst script file of the package. The command:\n\ngetent group hadoop 2>/dev/null >/dev/null || /usr/sbin/groupadd -g 123 -r hadoop\n\nshould be changed to:\n\ngetent group hadoop 2>/dev/null >/dev/null || /usr/sbin/addgroup -r hadoop","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=lsomchai","name":"lsomchai","key":"lsomchai","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?avatarId=10452","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&avatarId=10452","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&avatarId=10452","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&avatarId=10452"},"displayName":"Somchai LIMSIRORATANA","active":true,"timeZone":"Asia/Jakarta"},"created":"2014-01-11T10:29:00.482+0000","updated":"2014-01-11T10:29:00.482+0000"},{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/12604210/comment/14133337","id":"14133337","author":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=aw","name":"aw","key":"aw","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681"},"displayName":"Allen Wittenauer","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Tijuana"},"body":"Closing as won't fix as we no longer distributed packaged software.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/user?username=aw","name":"aw","key":"aw","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681","24x24":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=small&ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681","16x16":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=xsmall&ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681","32x32":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/useravatar?size=medium&ownerId=aw&avatarId=23681"},"displayName":"Allen Wittenauer","active":true,"timeZone":"America/Tijuana"},"created":"2014-09-14T18:41:43.702+0000","updated":"2014-09-14T18:41:43.702+0000"}],"maxResults":4,"total":4,"startAt":0},"votes":{"self":"https://issues.apache.org/jira/rest/api/2/issue/HADOOP-8716/votes","votes":2,"hasVoted":false},"worklog":{"startAt":0,"maxResults":20,"total":0,"worklogs":[]},"customfield_12311820":"0|i07sm7:"}}